Description: Distiller SDK - Universal ARM64 SDK for hardware control
 The Distiller SDK provides a self-contained Python environment with
 modules, model files, and native libraries for audio, camera, e-ink display,
 and TTS/ASR capabilities.
 .
 This universal package automatically detects and configures for:
  - Raspberry Pi CM5
  - Radxa Zero 3/3W (RK3566)
 .
 Platform detection is performed at installation time using device tree
 information. The correct GPIO pins and SPI device are configured automatically.
 Manual override is supported via the DISTILLER_PLATFORM environment variable.
